I understand why people would think all the colors would bleed together when washed, but I would not have a full book of returning clients if that were the case. These are just some of the colors I’ve done on my bestfriend over the past year and a half. Here’s some tips for at home care: wash in cold water using shampoo meant for vivids, only washing 1-2 times a week, little to no heat styling (and if you do, use a heat protectant!), no swimming with your head under water (of any kind; pools, lakes, oceans) and hats in the sun.
